FBIS4-13498 "drnes077_n_94015" FBIS-NES-94-077 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 LEBANON Minister Franjiyah Appointed LBC Political Supervisor Minister Franjiyah Appointed LBC Political Supervisor NC2104062094 Beirut AL-DIYAR in Arabic 14 Apr 94 p 1 NC2104062094 Beirut AL-DIYAR Arabic BFN [Text] Sulayman Franjiyah, minister of state for municipal and rural affairs, told AL-DIYAR that an agreement has been reached for him to assume the political supervision [al-ishraf al-siyasi] of the Lebanese Broadcasting Corporation [LBC]. Franjiyah denied that he has purchased shares in the corporation. Minister Franjiyah expects that the law reorganizing audio and visual media will be issued within a period not exceeding one and a half months.
